channel.title: Dictionary of Kink Terminology :: Safety Third
channel.description: General Terms Service (Role) or Service-Type Any individual that takes on a role (top/bottom, dom/sub, etc.) for the benefit of another. Note: Motivations for being a Service-Type varies between individuals, although general consensus is that they find enjoyment in being able to provide the service, and not directly from the act itself. Kink Relationship Dynamics +++
